snippet.title: Pirates of the Caribbean 5 Trailer Reaction
snippet.description:
Pirates of the Caribbean 5 Trailer Reaction today! Beyond The Trailer's reaction & review! Official! Dead Men Tell No Tales! Jack Sparrow!
http://bit.ly/subscribeBTT

Pirates of the Caribbean 5 Trailer Reaction today! Beyond The Trailer host Grace Randolph's reaction and review of the official trailer for Dead Men Tell No Tales starring Johnny Depp as Jack Sparrow and Javier Bardam as Captain Salazar!  Share your own reaction to this trailer from Disney for Pirates of the Caribbean 5 before you see the full movie in 2017!  And be sure to make Beyond The Trailer your first stop for movie and entertainment news here on YouTube today!
